{
  "info": {
    "_postman_id": "tienda-universitaria-v1",
    "name": "Tienda Universitaria — API REST",
    "description": "Colección completa de endpoints para la Tienda Universitaria de Unimagdalena.\n\n**Uso:**\n1. Importar esta colección en Postman\n2. Crear un entorno con variable `baseUrl = http://localhost:8080`\n3. Ejecutar `Auth / Login` o `Auth / Register` — el token se guarda automáticamente en `{{token}}`\n4. Todos los demás requests usan `{{token}}` en el header Authorization",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
  },
  "variable": [
    {
      "key": "baseUrl",
      "value": "http://localhost:8080",
      "type": "string"
    },
    {
      "key": "token",
      "value": "",
      "type": "string"
    }
  ],
  "item": [
    {
      "name": "Auth",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Register",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{"key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json"}],
            "url": {"raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/auth/register", "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"], "path": ["api", "auth", "register"]},
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"email\": \"usuario@test.com\",\n  \"password\": \"password123\"\n}"
            }
          },
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "var json = pm.response.json();",
                  "if (json.accessToken) {",
                  "  pm.collectionVariables.set('token', json.accessToken);",
                  "}"
                ]
              }
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "name": "Login",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{"key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json"}],
            "url": {"raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/auth/login", "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"], "path": ["api", "auth", "login"]},
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"email\": \"usuario@test.com\",\n  \"password\": \"password123\"\n}"
            }
          },
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "var json = pm.response.json();",
                  "if (json.accessToken) {",
                  "  pm.collectionVariables.set('token', json.accessToken);",
                  "  console.log('Token guardado:', json.accessToken.substring(0, 30) + '...');",
                  "}"
                ]
              }
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
